author: R.Q Aunelds
title: Jlacce
content: I would like to stop smoking cigarettes because people who smoke get emphysema, lung cancer, and the cit. The small bronchi get clogged. The debris allows dirt and the substances to enter the lungs. The air sacs become like rubber. What would your mother have in this world, a lot of smoke or a lot of deaths?
name: g'll Hocdre
